        <Parent_String>Tibetan painting styles [300114529], Tibetan (culture or style) [300018849], Himalayan [300018815], South Asian [300120222], Asian [300018279], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
